VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT \bIsolate\.spawnUri\s*\(
WHEN EXPR PRESENT:http://|https://|Uri\.parse.*http && MISSING:// trusted|// internal
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects Isolate.spawnUri calls pointing to remote HTTP/HTTPS URIs.
TRACE Externalized mobile rule logic for Isolate.spawnUri with Remote URI.
